  "instructions": [
    "heat the olive oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "add the chopped onion and cook until translucent, about 3 minutes.",
    "add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "add the brussels sprouts and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "add the lemon juice, orange juice, salt, black pepper, and red pepper flakes, and stir to combine.",
    "add the chicken broth and cook until the liquid has almost completely evaporated, about 2 minutes.",
    "stir in the chopped fresh parsley and mint.",
    "serve immediately and enjoy!"
